Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The time will come
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的时刻将会来临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when,with elation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你得意洋洋地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you will greet yourself arriving at your own door,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,站在自家门口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in your own mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,照着镜子迎接自我的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and each will smile at the other's welcome,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,以欢笑迎接彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and say, sit here. Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,并说道，坐这儿。吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You will love again the stranger who was your self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你将会再次爱上这个陌生人————从前的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give wine.Give bread.Give back your heart to itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,斟满美酒。递上面包。把心交还其身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to the stranger who has loved you all your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,给那一辈子爱着你的陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,whom you ignored for another,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾因为他人而忽略了他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,who knows you by heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他却打心底里懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take down the love letters from the bookshelf,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,从书架上取下那些情书
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the protographs, the desperate notes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,照片以及绝望的字条
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,peel your own image from the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,从镜中剥去自己的形象。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit. Feast on your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下。尽享你的生活
